                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/smk/press-center/Press-releases/2010/Treaty-between-Norway-and-Russia-to-be-signed.html?id=613684" title="">
                        Treaty between Norway and Russia to be signed
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[06.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Norway and Russia will sign the Treaty concerning Maritime Delimitation and Cooperation in the Barents Sea and the Arctic Ocean in Murmansk on 15 September. </p>
                
                
