                    <a href="/en/dep/smk/press-center/Press-releases/2010/state-secretary-to-leave-oed-for-hod.html?id=610253" title="">
                        State secretary to leave OED for HOD
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[25.06.2010]</p>
                <p>In today’s session of the Council of State the King has honourably dismissed Mr. Robin Kåss from his office as state secretary to Minister of Petroleum and Energy Terje Riis-Johansen, and at the same time appointed him as state secretary to Minister of Health and Care Services Anne-Grete Strøm-Erichsen. </p>
                
                
