            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/smk/press-center/Press-releases/2010/Changes-among-the-state-secretaries1.html?id=609028" title="">
                        Changes among the state secretaries
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[18.06.2010]</p>
                <p>State State Secretary Espen Barth Eide has been transferred from the Ministry of Defence to the Ministry of Foreign Affairs, while State Secretary Roger Ingebrigtsen has been transferred from the Ministry of Health and Care to the Ministry of Defence. The changes are effective as of 28 June 2010.</p>
                
                
